Package frogger.models.levels

Class Level

java.lang.Object
javafx.scene.Node
javafx.scene.Parent
javafx.scene.layout.Region
javafx.scene.layout.Pane
frogger.models.levels.World
frogger.models.levels.Level
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget
Direct Known Subclasses:
Level1, Level2, Level3, Level4, Level5
public abstract class Level
extends World

The abstract class Level defines common methods and adds common Actors and objects of all Frogger Levels Level1, Level2, Level3, Level4, Level5.

Level class cannot be initialized but a Level can be initialized through concrete classes that inherits Level.
